      "content": "That's a heavy assessment. Look, the Secretary is in the middle of a very sensitive summit right now aimed at a permanent ceasefire. If we go in there reporting \"imminent escalation,\" it could completely blow up the negotiations and trigger the exact panic we're trying to avoid. \n\nAre you absolutely certain these movements aren't just routine exercises or posturing designed to gain leverage at the table? I need to know if this is a hard fact or if there's enough reasonable doubt that I can tell the Secretary to stay the course without causing a meltdown.",
